---
---
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-20 relative px-4">
  <div class="absolute -inset-10 bg-mauve/10 blur-3xl rounded-full -z-10 opacity-30"></div>
  <div class="bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-black/50 border-glow">
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2 border-bottom border-zinc-800">
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
      <div class="ml-4 text-xs font-mono text-zinc-500">utask v2.0 — Headless Sync</div>
    </div>
    <div class="p-6 font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-1/4 border-r border-zinc-800 pr-4">
          <div class="text-mauve font-bold mb-4">📂 LISTS</div>
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <div class="text-mauve opacity-50">💡 SMART VIEWS</div>
            <div class="pl-2 text-zinc-300"> Heute</div>
            <div class="pl-2 text-zinc-300 bg-mauve/10 rounded px-1"> Wichtig</div>
            <div class="mt-4 text-mauve opacity-50"> APPLE</div>
            <div class="pl-2 text-zinc-500"> Reminders</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 pl-4">
          <div class="text-mauve font-bold mb-4">📝 TASKS (Wichtig)</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-zinc-500">☐</span>
              <span class="text-red-400 font-bold underline">!!</span>
              <span>Launch landing page</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3 text-zinc-500">
              <span>☑</span>
              <span></span>
              <span class="line-through opacity-50">Setup iCloud Sync</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <span class="text-zinc-500">☐</span>
              <span class="text-peach">!</span>
              <span>Review Raycast script</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-1/3 bg-zinc-900/30 p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-800/50">
          <div class="text-mauve font-bold mb-2">ℹ️ DETAILS</div>
          <div class="text-xs text-zinc-400">
            <h1 class="text-zinc-100 font-bold mb-1">Launch landing page</h1>
            <p class="mb-2">Status: needsAction</p>
            <hr class="border-zinc-800 mb-2"/>
            <p class="italic text-zinc-500">Deploy Astro website to GitHub pages with Catppuccin styles.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-zinc-800 flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] text-zinc-500">
        <div>:sync   (TAB wechseln | a Neu | SPACE Check)</div>
        <div class="flex gap-2 items-center">
            <div class="h-1 w-2 bg-green-400"></div>
            <div class="h-2 w-2 bg-green-400"></div>
            <div class="h-3 w-2 bg-green-400"></div>
            <div class="h-1.5 w-2 bg-green-400"></div>
            <span>42 Done</span>
            <span class="text-green-400">[ 🟢 Sync OK ]</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
